full_text: Screened by NARA, 9/13/2023 U.S. Department of State OMB APPROVAL NO. 1405-0015 EXPIRES: 07/31/2007 ESTIMATED BURDEN: 1 HOUR* (See Page 2) APPLICATION FOR IMMIGRANT VISA AND ALIEN REGISTRATION PART I - BIOGRAPHIC DATA INSTRUCTIONS: Complete one copy of this form for yourself and each member of your family, regardless of age, who will immigrate with you. Please print or type your answers to all questions. Mark questions that are Not Applicable with "N/A". If there is insufficient room on the form, answer on a separate sheet using the same numbers that appear on the form. Attach any additional sheets to this form. WARNING: Any false statement or concealment of a material fact may result in your permanent exclusion from the United States. This form (DS-230 PART I) is the first of two parts. This part, together with Form DS-230 PART II, constitutes the complete Application for Immigrant Visa and Alien Registration. 1. Family Name First Demders Name "Sesperance" Middle Name 2.
